107
00:03:44,710 --> 00:03:45,710
in disputed waters.

108
00:03:45,710 --> 00:03:48,000
He said: 'Well if you force the issue,

109
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:51,510
we'll be forced to tell you the truth.

110
00:03:51,510 --> 00:03:52,510
What is the truth?

111
00:03:52,510 --> 00:03:53,870
We will go to war.

112
00:03:53,870 --> 00:03:56,440
We will fight you.

113
00:03:56,440 --> 00:03:58,990
And despite what Duterte said last October...

114
00:03:58,990 --> 00:04:01,200
I will break up with America.

115
00:04:01,200 --> 00:04:04,530
I would rather go to Russia and to China.

116
00:04:04,530 --> 00:04:07,760
...now he seems to be asking for US help.

117
00:04:07,760 --> 00:04:09,760
So we seek the help of America,

118
00:04:09,760 --> 00:04:14,110
a concerted effort of all the member states

119
00:04:14,110 --> 00:04:16,741
of the United Nations,

120
00:04:16,741 --> 00:04:17,741
