121
00:04:17,741 --> 00:04:18,741
Because if they're willing to fight

122
00:04:18,741 --> 00:04:19,741
then we are,

123
00:04:19,741 --> 00:04:20,950
but if it was only me,

124
00:04:20,950 --> 00:04:25,220
why would I do that?

125
00:04:25,220 --> 00:04:26,630
It will result in a massacre

126
00:04:26,630 --> 00:04:31,810
